thread.title: Jimmy Grice
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Jimmy Grice

author: Jimmy Grice
title: Jimmy Grice
text: When we arrived, they had our car ready to go, ran us through everything and we were off within 15 minutes. When we delivered the car back, we had a shuttle to take us to the airport there and then. Very seamless processes. I recommend Omega highly and will be definitely using them again.
